OL,3,CDrink driver killed partner in crash
OL,4,Cafter drinking 'lager, rum and wine'
OL,6,FA woman crashed her car into a shop
OL,7,Fwhile more than twice the drink drive
OL,8,Flimit, killing her partner, has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FLucy Pegler drank lager, rum, wine and
OL,12,Fother alcohol before getting behind
OL,13,Fthe wheel of her Fiat 500 to drive her
OL,14,Fpartner Kyle Shimwell and two other
OL,15,Ffriends home following a night out in
OL,16,FBakewell.
OL,18,FAs she drove along King Street, police
OL,19,Fsaid she failed to negotiate a slight
OL,20,Fbend, mounted a kerb and collided with
OL,21,Fthe front of a shop.
