OL,3,CDrink driver killed partner in crash
OL,4,Cafter drinking 'lager, rum and wine'
OL,6,FOfficers said Mr Shimwell, who was the
OL,7,Ffront seat passenger, and was not
OL,8,Fwearing a seatbelt, suffered serious
OL,9,Finjuries after the collision which
OL,10,Foccurred on 7 January 23.
OL,12,FHe was taken to the Northern General
OL,13,FHospital in Sheffield where he died
OL,14,Ftwo days later on 9 January, aged 21.
OL,16,FIn a victim personal statement read
OL,17,Fout at court, Mr Shimwell's father
OL,18,Fsaid: "I cannot put into words the
OL,19,Fhurt and pain losing Kyle has
OL,20,Finflicted on our lives.
