OL,6,FHe said: "People keep on saying it
OL,7,Fwill get better over time. I'm
OL,8,Fstruggling to believe that. I think
OL,9,Fthe wound will heal in time but the
OL,10,Fscar that is left behind will be there
OL,11,Fforever.
OL,13,F"Kyle lost his life because of Lucy
OL,14,FPegler's decision to drink drive even
OL,15,Fthough the journey home would have
OL,16,Fbeen a ten-minute walk.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
