OL,3,CDrink driver killed partner in crash
OL,4,Cafter drinking 'lager, rum and wine'
OL,6,F"We as a family hope she receives the
OL,7,Ffull punishment she deserves not only
OL,8,Fto make her pay for what she has done,
OL,9,Fbut hopefully send a message out to
OL,10,Fothers of how that decision can take
OL,11,Flives and destroy others."
OL,13,FPegler failed a roadside breath test
OL,14,Ffollowing the crash and was arrested
OL,15,Fat the scene. She was later found to
OL,16,Fbe more than twice the legal limit.
OL,18,FThe 22-year-old, of East Bank,
OL,19,FWinster, was later charged with
OL,20,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
