OL,6,FShe initially denied the charge before
OL,7,Fpleading guilty in August 2024 to
OL,8,Fcausing death through careless driving
OL,9,Fand while unfit through drink.
OL,11,FShe appeared at Derby Crown Court for
OL,12,Fsentence on 26 September when she was
OL,13,Fjailed for four and half years.
